  <!-- Heavy Equipment Training -->
  <item>
    <title>Heavy Equipment Training</title>
    <link>http://tricountydrivingacademy.com/courses/heavy-equipment-training/</link>
    <pubDate>Thu, 01 Jan 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
    <dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
    <content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Construction is a thriving business in constant need of safe, competent heavy equipment operators.</p>
<p>Get the knowledge and skills to operate equipment such as dozers, end loaders, excavators, and back-hoes.</p>
<h3>Program Details</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Program Length:</strong> 4 weeks</li>
  <li><strong>Schedule:</strong> Classes start monthly</li>
  <li><strong>Price:</strong> $4,250 (includes tuition &amp; books)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Equipment Covered</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Bulldozers / Dozers</li>
  <li>End Loaders / Wheel Loaders</li>
  <li>Excavators</li>
  <li>Back-hoes</li>
  <li>Safety procedures and OSHA compliance</li>
</ul>
<p>Pell Grant packages available. Contact us at 276-794-7660 for details.</p>
    ]]></content:encoded>
