  <!-- Fiber Optics Training -->
  <item>
    <title>Fiber Optics Training</title>
    <link>http://tricountydrivingacademy.com/courses/fiber-optics-training/</link>
    <pubDate>Thu, 01 Jan 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
    <dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
    <content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Fiber Optic design, installation and maintenance is a profession that will see increasing demands in the future.</p>
<p>Our course provides the student with the knowledge and skills to become a Fiber Optic Assembler or Installer/Technician.</p>
<h3>Program Details</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Program Length:</strong> 3 weeks</li>
  <li><strong>Schedule:</strong> Classes start monthly</li>
  <li><strong>Price:</strong> $2,500 (includes tuition, books &amp; supplies)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Topics Covered</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Fiber optic theory and terminology</li>
  <li>Cable types and connectors</li>
  <li>Splicing and termination techniques</li>
  <li>Testing and troubleshooting</li>
  <li>Safety practices</li>
</ul>
    ]]></content:encoded>
