  <!-- Diesel School -->
  <item>
    <title>Diesel School</title>
    <link>http://tricountydrivingacademy.com/courses/diesel-school/</link>
    <pubDate>Thu, 01 Jan 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
    <dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
    <content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Our Diesel School program provides comprehensive training in diesel engine repair and heavy truck maintenance.</p>
<h3>Program Details</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Program Length:</strong> 11 months</li>
  <li><strong>Price:</strong> $21,500 (includes tuition, books &amp; supplies)</li>
  <li><strong>Financial Aid:</strong> Available for Virginia residents</li>
</ul>
<h3>Topics Covered</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Diesel engines and fuel injection systems</li>
  <li>Transmissions and drive trains</li>
  <li>Computerized systems diagnostics</li>
  <li>Truck electrical systems</li>
  <li>Brakes, suspension, and steering</li>
  <li>Preventive maintenance procedures</li>
</ul>
<p>Financial aid is available for our Virginia Residents. Please call our office at 276-794-7660 for more information.</p>
    ]]></content:encoded>
